        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/bervo/BERVO_9000004"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>The rate at which argon molecules or atoms move through gaseous or aqueous media due to concentration gradients and molecular motion. This parameter is used as a conservative tracer for studying gas transport processes in terrestrial and aquatic systems.</obo:IAO_0000115>
