        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/bervo/BERVO_9000004"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>The rate at which carbon dioxide molecules move through gaseous or aqueous media due to concentration gradients and molecular transport processes. This parameter is fundamental for modeling carbon dioxide exchange between ecosystems and the atmosphere and carbon cycling in terrestrial and aquatic environments.</obo:IAO_0000115>
