        <obo:IAO_0000115>The rate at which nitrogen gas molecules move through gaseous or aqueous media due to concentration gradients and molecular transport processes. This parameter is important for modeling nitrogen fixation and denitrification processes and nitrogen exchange between terrestrial ecosystems and the atmosphere.</obo:IAO_0000115>
