        <obo:IAO_0000115>The rate at which nitrous oxide molecules move through gaseous or aqueous media due to concentration gradients and molecular transport processes. This parameter is crucial for modeling greenhouse gas emissions from soils and understanding nitrous oxide dynamics in terrestrial and aquatic ecosystems.</obo:IAO_0000115>
