    <Class rdf:about="https://w3id.org/bervo/BERVO_8000388">
        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/bervo/BERVO_8000529"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>The classification or category of a nucleic acid or protein sequence such as DNA, RNA, or amino acid sequences. Sequence type designation specifies the chemical nature and interpretation of sequence data.</obo:IAO_0000115>
