        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/bervo/BERVO_8000232"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A text narrative providing explanatory details about an object, process, or observation. Descriptions document context, methods, and characteristics necessary for interpretation and reproducibility.</obo:IAO_0000115>
