        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/bervo/BERVO_8000232"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A uniform resource identifier (URI) such as a DOI (Digital Object Identifier) or URL (Uniform Resource Locator) referencing external data or publications. Links enable access to related information and data provenance.</obo:IAO_0000115>
