    <Class rdf:about="https://w3id.org/bervo/BERVO_8000392">
        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/bervo/BERVO_8000232"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>The category of methodology employed to generate data, including sequencing, spectroscopy, cultivation, or measurement techniques. Experimental process classification enables assessment of method-specific biases and comparability.</obo:IAO_0000115>
