        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/bervo/BERVO_8000232"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A geographic point or area where observations, measurements, or samples are collected or sourced. Location information is essential for spatial analysis and environmental characterization.</obo:IAO_0000115>
