        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/bervo/BERVO_8000394"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>The angular distance east or west of the Prime Meridian measured in degrees, minutes, and seconds (or decimal degrees). Longitude specifies the east-west coordinate in geographic positioning systems.</obo:IAO_0000115>
