        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/bervo/BERVO_8000232"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A coordinate reference system that uses a map projection to represent locations on a curved surface as planar coordinates, enabling positions to be expressed as easting and northing values in linear units. A projected coordinate system includes a base geographic coordinate system, projection method, datum, linear unit, and projection parameters; examples include UTM Zone 13N and State Plane zones.</obo:IAO_0000115>
