        <rdfs:comment>Definition revised to generalize the previous State plane zone term to projected coordinate systems that can qualify easting and northing values.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment>Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025).  JMC manually edited label and definition on 3/23/26</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>Projected Coordinate System</rdfs:label>
        <bervo:BERVO_Attribute rdf:resource="NA"/>
        <bervo:BERVO_Context rdf:resource="NA"/>
        <bervo:BERVO_Qualifier rdf:resource="NA"/>
